What is CloudTrail?
Tracks all AWS account activities.

Why CloudTrail?
Answer questions like:

Who deleted EC2?
Who modified Security Group?
Who created IAM User?

Architecture:
User Action
      ↓
CloudTrail
      ↓
Log Stored

Example Event:
User: Developer1

Action:
Terminate EC2

Time:
10:35 AM

CloudTrail records everything.

Real-Time Scenario:
Production outage occurs.

Investigation team checks:

CloudTrail Logs

to identify root cause.

Benefits:
Compliance
Auditing
Security Investigation
Governance
